 gauge coupling\nconstant is non-zero in the \"late\" Universe, i.e., charge confinement is\noperating, whereas it vanishes in the \"early\" Universe, i.e., confinement-free\nepoch; (iv) The unification of dark energy and dark matter is explicitly seen\nwithin the FLRW reduction, where they appear as dynamically generated effective\nvacuum energy density and dynamically induced dust-like matter,\ncorrespondingly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Jan 2018 18:33:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-30"}
