 being perfect. We also relate dual integrality of an SDP formulation for\nthe maximum cut problem to bipartite graphs. Total dual integrality for\nextended formulations naturally comes into play in this context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Jan 2018 00:14:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-30"}
